{"tid":2415273,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC/Steam]GTFO","createTime":"2021-02-20T06:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T10:54:15.000Z","uid":35056,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"64bfd3155f7f736f73824bcea85a39e5a368b4fb","tid":2415273,"uid":35056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:36:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/53/65c654c7699da33f511fa8fe711784x5.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F53%2F65c654c7699da33f511fa8fe711784x5.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=bf8c8181&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《GTFO》是一款極度講求合作的恐怖射擊遊戲，遊戲中玩家將要扮演囚人，被要求進入極度危險的地下深處，帶回目標物品。一路上會有許多人型的異形生物分布在各個區域，玩家必須與其他三名玩家合作，以各種手段把目標帶回。遊戲講求的是極度緊繃的遊戲氛圍，在遊戲中所探索到的補給物資以及彈藥是非常有限的。因此玩家必須時刻與隊友溝通好每一個房間該怎麼進攻、防守、每一個敵人該怎麼打倒，才能以最小的資源獲得最高的報酬。<br />\n<br />\n之前見過有巴打開過dc谷,最後無哂聲氣<br />\n想招有興趣既巴絲組隊<br />\n主要係放工後可能打一兩場/假期,六,日打<br />\n希望招到隊友一齊慢慢攻略<br />\ndc link:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4268f20d1803393dc09ff2d3f22cbc3fea45d648","tid":2415273,"uid":35056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:36:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cefde55f9a15b9528d880737660a0be991ca9588","tid":2415273,"uid":35056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:46:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"238f86f5399954b74270eb384bda232e0b16cb97","tid":2415273,"uid":35056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:38:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86f332f91c4de6e7d703555d4cd507a63439ab0e","tid":2415273,"uid":35056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:58:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b51a236d5a95760628496eeb47795368d6b04b","tid":2415273,"uid":32433,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T08:22:06.000Z","msg":"好似唔錯, lm"},{"pid":"0d5904c850f8a15ba6d599c21c4839305897dd4b","tid":2415273,